            </p>
            <h3>Key Aspects of Regulatory Compliance:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Accessibility Compliance:</strong> PolyTransport follows accessibility guidelines to ensure that the bus system is inclusive and accessible to all students, including those with special needs.</li>
                <li><strong>Data Protection:</strong> Stringent measures are in place to protect user data and privacy. PolyTransport complies with data protection regulations, implementing encryption and secure storage practices.</li>
                <li><strong>Health and Safety Protocols:</strong> The system adheres to established health and safety protocols. This includes measures to prevent the spread of infectious diseases and ensure the well-being of passengers and staff.</li>
                <li><strong>Collaboration with Authorities:</strong> PolyTransport collaborates with local transportation authorities to stay informed about regulatory updates. This proactive approach ensures ongoing compliance with evolving standards.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                By prioritizing regulatory compliance, PolyTransport aims to provide a transportation solution that aligns with the highest industry standards and legal requirements.
            </p>
        </section>

